congress ludvigson is hoping someone will spot the flasher and 
decide to market it 
people come to the congress which has been held annually in 
redwood falls since 1958 not only to get exposure and to market 
their ideas but also to find direction 
others come to get the publics reaction to their inventions 
said andrew amoroso a business development specialist from the 
