missiles 
the missiles and their camouflaged launchers positioned at this 
base in remote southeastern sicily are stored under tons of earth 
and concrete and surrounded by four rows of chainlink fence topped 
with barbed wire 
soviet inspectors will arrive sometime after july 1 to count the 
