gorbachevs program which seeks to reform the soviet economy and 
social system 
we are looking for a tax system to stimulate innovation and 
how to use taxes to get work collectives to use the socialist 
property in the best way senchagov told a news conference 
speaking through an interpreter he said the danger of 
